Interface LoggingEventRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<LoggingEvent,Long>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<LoggingEvent,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<LoggingEvent,Long>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<LoggingEvent>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<LoggingEvent,Long>
public interface LoggingEventRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<LoggingEvent,Long>
LoggingEventRepository is repository for JPA with LoggingEvent

An immutable repository is only used to read data written by logback-spring DbAppender
